Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.56,0:00:22.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Hello, everyone! \N Welcome to the Pokémon Resort!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.56,0:00:26.06,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I’m Haru, your concierge!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.19,0:00:29.40,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,On this island \N overflowing with nature,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.40,0:00:35.65,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Pokémon and trainers alike can engage in \N all sorts of activities and relaxation.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.23,0:00:45.15,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,As your concierges, we’ll be devoted to helping you, \N to ensure that you’re all free to unwind.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.02,0:00:50.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Please enjoy your stay \N at the Pokémon Resort!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.98,0:00:51.60,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.60,0:00:53.15,Main,Guest,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.98,0:01:25.23,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Hey, Haru!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.23,0:01:26.81,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Tyler-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.81,0:01:29.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,All that luggage...\N Are you heading out on the ship?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.77,0:01:30.81,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.81,0:01:34.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Wait, does that mean... \Nyou’re off work today, {\i1}too?{\i0}{To be clear: She means it as in "Tyler is also away today in addition to Watanabe and Alisa", not as in "Geez Tyler, you've been off work for days and now you're saying you'll be off AGAIN?" -TLC}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.31,0:01:36.48,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,{Nah}Oh, I’m {gonna be }working!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.48,0:01:38.31,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,I’m gonna stock up on berries!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.77,0:01:41.52,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh? \N Weren’t you doing that next month?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.52,0:01:46.52,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,{\q2}That was the plan, but then I got a call outta nowhere \N this morning saying to come grab ‘em today!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.52,0:01:50.48,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,B-But Alisa isn’t back \N until tomorrow, is she?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.48,0:01:51.90,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Yeah, that’s right!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.90,0:01:54.19,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,It’s her sister’s wedding today, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.19,0:01:56.73,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,She deserves to \N take it easy for once, eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.73,0:02:00.81,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,‘Kay, you handle the rest, will ya? \N Good luck!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.81,0:02:03.06,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.77,0:02:08.31,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Well, Watanabe-san’s coming back from \N her business trip today, so you’ll be fine, yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.31,0:02:10.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh?! You can’t make it back?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.31,0:02:14.10,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,I’m afraid not. \N I haven’t even made it out of the hotel yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.10,0:02:15.73,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,There’s a terrible storm here.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.23,0:02:17.73,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.73,0:02:21.98,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,But Kolynk and Roentorar are supposed to \N make their first visit today, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.98,0:02:24.77,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,I’ll try my best to be back \N by the afternoon.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.15,0:02:33.06,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Watanabe-san, feel free to \N stay where you are for today!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.06,0:02:33.98,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.40,0:02:36.60,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,We don’t want you getting injured, \N after all!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.60,0:02:39.44,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,One way or another, \N I’ll manage on my own.{Two other tries if this feels like it's changing the nuance: I'll make it work by myself. | I'll find a way to manage on my own. - Toa}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.19,0:02:41.48,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.48,0:02:43.48,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I am! Leave it all to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.19,0:02:45.69,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.15,0:02:50.40,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Thank you. \N I’ll be counting on you, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.40,0:02:54.48,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,If you need something, \N ask the receptionist and she’ll help.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.48,0:02:57.15,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,The Pokémon, I’m sure, \N will also be there for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.60,0:02:58.90,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.10,0:03:05.40,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Let’s see... “For Baoppe’s food, \N fry all the way through”...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.40,0:03:11.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,And the ones I peeled before, \N I’m supposed to fry in oil, then blanch them, and...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.98,0:03:12.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.69,0:03:14.52,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,No, Yabukuron!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.90,0:03:17.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Oh, sheesh!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.15,0:03:25.35,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Won’t you two \N try and get along?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.15,0:03:27.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,What’s wrong, Roentorar?
Comment: 10,0:03:27.69,0:03:33.44,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.44,0:03:41.44,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh? The fire...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.19,0:03:43.44,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Mizugorou!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.44,0:03:45.44,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.44,0:03:46.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,But why are you here?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.98,0:03:50.90,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Oh, right! \N I have to go to the vegetable patch!
Comment: 10,0:04:00.44,0:04:01.60,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.94,0:04:05.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Oh, Digda!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.94,0:04:12.27,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I {\i1}just{\i0} planted seeds there!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.27,0:04:12.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.94,0:04:15.27,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ah! Roentorar, don’t dig holes!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.31,0:04:18.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Kolynk, Mizugorou, calm down!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.56,0:04:21.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Koduck, wait a sec!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.98,0:04:30.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Kairyu! Pidgeot, you too!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.02,0:04:41.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Sorry, but could you \N play somewhere else today?
Comment: 10,0:04:56.52,0:04:57.15,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.69,0:04:59.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Eevee? What’s the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.35,0:05:02.15,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgot!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.77,0:05:07.40,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,There you have it! \N Your summer cut!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.40,0:05:09.90,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,A {real }nice, refreshing look!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.44,0:05:15.10,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.40,0:05:17.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,How’s this?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.94,0:05:19.60,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Bam!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.60,0:05:23.44,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,It looks wonderful on you, \N dear guest!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.02,0:05:28.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.94,0:05:30.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,It’s okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.31,0:05:32.19,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I’m just going to clip your nails.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.19,0:05:33.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,It won’t hurt!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.85,0:06:15.15,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,At this rate, \N I’ll never last the whole day...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.23,0:06:19.85,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Your paw’s like a little hand, \N it’s so nice.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.48,0:06:23.60,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Hand... Oh, of course! \N You just {\i1}handed{\i0} me an idea!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.60,0:06:25.56,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Everybody, please lend me a hand!
Comment: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:26.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.23,0:06:38.56,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Wow, Heigani! \N You’re so good at massages!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.31,0:07:04.40,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ouch, it’s hot!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.40,0:07:05.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ah! That’s perfect!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.98,0:07:08.40,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Thank you, Roentorar and Kolynk!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.98,0:07:12.06,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I’d like to call you “Chef” from now on, \N if you don’t mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.48,0:07:19.48,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,“Even a Pokémon’s assistance comes in handy,” \N isn’t that so?{Clearly punning on "neko no te mo karitai", figuratively "I'll take all the help I'll get, from wherever," but literally "Even wanting cats to lend a hand." -TLC}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.48,0:07:24.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I’m so glad you guys \N have enjoyed helping me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.60,0:07:30.10,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,But I must say...\N Tyler-san, Alisa, and Watanabe-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.10,0:07:35.40,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,They always look like they’re having fun with work, \N but they’ve actually been working really hard, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.40,0:07:40.06,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Behind that fun, \N there’s a lot of effort,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.06,0:07:44.65,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,and the effort is {being held up}driven \N by that {very same fun}very fun itself.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.23,0:07:47.27,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,What? What?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.81,0:07:49.56,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh? Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.60,0:07:55.73,Main,Front Desk,0,0,0,,Yes? This is reception.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.73,0:07:58.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Oh, thank goodness! \N I finally got through!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.77,0:08:00.40,Main,Front Desk,0,0,0,,Oh, Haru-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.40,0:08:03.81,Main,Front Desk,0,0,0,,The whole island’s had a blackout! \N We’re in a bind!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.81,0:08:06.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,What could have happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.31,0:08:09.73,Main,Front Desk,0,0,0,,Sounds like the power storage device \N might’ve malfunctioned.
Comment: 10,0:08:09.23,0:08:09.73,Main,Man,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.73,0:08:12.31,Main,Front Desk,0,0,0,,Apparently power’s \N stopped coming through.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.31,0:08:14.81,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,What?! No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.81,0:08:17.35,Main,Front Desk,0,0,0,,If we can restart it, \N it should work again.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.81,Main,Front Desk,0,0,0,,But we already \N have our hands full here.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.81,0:08:21.94,Main,Front Desk,0,0,0,,Could you please handle it, \N Haru-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.94,0:08:23.48,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,What? Me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,But can I even...?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.77,0:08:29.85,Main,Front Desk,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Wait, Gänger! \N C-Calm down! Ahh!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.73,0:08:44.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.73,0:08:50.60,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.35,0:08:53.35,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,And next...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.35,0:08:54.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.35,0:08:58.27,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,This is the switch \N I should flip, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.85,0:09:01.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Now to restart!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.27,0:09:10.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Wha...?! Why?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.19,0:09:12.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,What do I do now?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.35,0:09:15.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,The sun’s about to set...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.15,0:09:19.06,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,It looks like the windmill \N can generate electricity, too...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.06,0:09:21.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,If only there was wind...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.73,0:09:24.60,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.27,0:09:28.85,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,If there’s no wind, \N we can just stir some up!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.27,0:09:38.27,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Kairyu! Pidgeot! If you would!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.27,0:09:53.40,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,It’s moving!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.27,0:10:02.65,Main,Front Desk,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.60,0:10:07.90,Main,Front Desk,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.69,0:10:09.69,Main,Front Desk,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.40,0:10:21.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.94,0:10:25.56,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Thank you for working so hard! \N You’ve done more than enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.27,0:10:36.65,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Is that...?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.48,0:10:40.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Kolynk! Roentorar! \N Are you gonna help?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.94,0:10:43.23,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Okay, we’re good to go!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.10,0:10:47.44,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Well then... Please go ahead!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.27,0:11:02.44,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Yes! It’s charging!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.94,0:11:11.65,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.94,0:11:20.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,It’s just like I thought... \N I couldn’t do a thing on my own...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.69,0:11:25.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I’m sure Tyler-san would take control \N of the situation and get us out of it easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.94,0:11:29.23,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,And Alisa would come up \N with some brilliant idea, too...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.23,0:11:31.10,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,And Watanabe-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.10,0:11:34.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I don’t know how, \N but I’m sure she’d solve it, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.73,0:11:39.73,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,And the Pokémon were \N nice enough to help me out, too...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.27,0:11:42.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Everyone must be \N having a tough time.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.69,0:11:45.15,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.02,0:11:47.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,What’s that?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.06,0:12:00.48,Main,Guest,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.48,0:12:02.06,Main,Guest,0,0,0,,It’s beautiful.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.06,0:12:03.90,Main,Guest,0,0,0,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.48,0:12:11.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.10,0:12:17.27,Main,Guest,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.56,0:12:22.52,Main,Guest,0,0,0,,Kabigon!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.15,0:12:27.65,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Pokémon are so amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.23,0:12:42.06,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Uh... Haru?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.06,0:12:44.90,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Why in the world \N are you sleeping out here?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.90,0:12:49.23,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Alisa!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.40,0:12:52.90,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,What happened? \N It’s only been a day...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.56,0:12:55.23,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Good mornin’, Haru!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.23,0:12:56.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Tyler-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.31,0:12:57.23,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.23,0:12:59.23,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,I’m back, Haru-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.23,0:13:00.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Watanabe-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.77,0:13:02.90,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Was the weather okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.90,0:13:05.98,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,It all cleared up as soon as \N I stepped out of the hotel.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.98,0:13:09.48,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,I had forgotten that \N I’m a real sunshine magnet!{Literally "an amazing clear skies woman". Incidentally the same term used to describe Hina in Tenki no Ko, if I don't remember wrong. -TLC}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.48,0:13:10.81,Main,Haru Alisa,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.35,0:13:14.81,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Looks to me like Kolynk and Roentorar \N have enjoyed themselves here.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.23,0:13:17.31,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,So, how was yesterday, Haru?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.31,0:13:20.40,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Lookin’ after the place alone? \N I heard you went through a lot, eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.40,0:13:23.06,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was so...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.35,0:13:30.15,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,It was so much fun, \N because the Pokémon were there with me!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.06,0:13:34.60,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Look at you, talking like that.{Literally "You've gotten to the point of saying such things, huh?" -TLC}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.60,0:13:37.27,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Well, you did great.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.27,0:13:38.77,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.77,0:13:40.15,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Here. A little souvenir.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.15,0:13:41.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.69,0:13:44.73,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,And this is from me. \N Keep it up, Haru.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.73,0:13:46.27,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,And here’s something from me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.27,0:13:49.23,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,You really did great. Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.23,0:13:51.73,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ooh, thank you so much!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.73,0:13:54.81,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh? These... are all chocolate!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.19,0:13:56.85,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Eh? For real?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.85,0:13:58.69,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Careful you don’t get cavities!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.65,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,My reward!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.15,0:14:11.06,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Wait, Koduck!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.85,0:14:20.19,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,All right, everyone! \N Let’s give it all we’ve got today!
Comment: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:21.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
